Author: vonnegutslut
Text: totally relate to face pretty vs body pretty. my self confidence has always been rock bottom but at least i have some control over being a “butterface” vs all around ugly and i feel like i’ve wasted my teenage and now my college years in an endless cycle of BP that never helps me lose enough weight to be happy and go out and enjoy life

Author: red_ossifrage
Text: omg faceapp sucks. Delete that shit! It's completely disconnected from reality, and mostly just seems to make people feel bad about themselves. It's pretty fucking arbitrary, in terms of how much the app filter decides to mess with your appearance...it seriously has very little to do with your actual looks.
